      • initialize

        public void initialize​(java.net.URL url,
                       java.util.ResourceBundle rb)
        The JavaFX initialize method.

        Lambda usage: This is the second case for lambda implementation for this project. We use lambda expressions over PropertyValueFactory to initialize the table data within their respective Customers TableView columns. We don't use a lambda expression for customerIdColumn because ReadOnlyIntegerWrapper() cannot be converted to ObservableValue.

        Specified by:
        initialize in interface javafx.fxml.Initializable
        Parameters:
        url - the url
        rb - the resource bundle
